There is neither chanting nor austerity in the Kali-yuga. Only the name of Rama is the only support of the creature in this Kalikala. Shri Ram Chandra ji is a simple, merciful and kind person, his name is the only one who gives life to the creature and is the ultimate welfare. Keeping this objective in mind, this website has been constructed. Our request to you is to chant the name of Ram as much as possible. In this, we all have welfare.


1,25,000 - All sins accumalated in this birth begin to be destroyed.


2,25,000 -The sins of life are destroyed and all evil houses start redressing.


5,00,000 -The devotion of the feet increases with the grace of Lord Rama.


10,00,000 -All sins of past lives are destroyed.


25,00,000 -The nightmare of life is eradicated and all the opulence part and the fruits of liberation are reaped.


50,00,000 -All kinds of virtues and yajna are reaped.


75,00,000 -Sins of many births is destroyed and unbroken devotion to Lord Rama is found.


1,00,00,000-The Ashwamedha yagna results in a double form are reaped.

Jai Siyaram ji devotees! This website has been created by the grace of Shri Hanuman Ji Maharaj Ji to write Ram Naam online. Over the years the name of Ram is generally written on the books, but in today's era, we have to put a little tireless effort in writing the name of Ram in office, train, bus or any other place, so this website has been created. Now you can write Ram Naam online anywhere and anytime.It's a humble request to all the devotees, please tell your experience and suggestions of writing Ram Naam so that we can make amendments in this website & make it better.
